  "title": "Jewellery Retail Sales Executive (Mass Hiring! Island-wide! High Comission!) - LCYL",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Jewellery Sales Assistant</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Working days: 4-5-4-5 days in rotation including PH, 10 off days per month</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Working hours: 10.30am to 9.45pm with 2 breaks</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Location: Islandwide</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Selling of gold jewellery, diamonds, and luxury goods</li>\n  <li>Attend to customers’ enquires and feedback</li>\n  <li>Provide excellent customer service and assistance to customers</li>\n  <li>Offer advice and guidance on product selections</li>\n  <li>Manage point-of-sale processes</li>\n  <li>Maintain good store condition and visual merchandising standards</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Must be willing to work on retail hours, weekend and public holiday</li>\n  <li>Keen in jewellery industry</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Cheong Yeat Long | R25145358</p>\n<p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | EA 14C7279</p>",
